# 🔍 PrivyShare (ShadowVault) — Updated Audit Report v2

> **Date:** March 12, 2026  
> **Scope:** Full re-audit after bug-fix pass — frontend, smart contract, encryption, IPFS, wallet  
> **Files Reviewed:** 45+ files across `app/`, `components/`, `lib/`, `contracts/`, config

