## ✅ What Was Fixed (Good Job!)

| Original Bug | Status | How It Was Fixed |
|---|---|---|
| Race condition in file registration | ✅ Fixed | Retry loop (3 attempts) with fresh [getFileCounter()](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/ShadowVault/lib/aleo/programState.ts#12-29) per attempt |
| Download with zeroed IV/salt | ✅ Fixed | Now requires IV & salt from user; shows error if missing |
| Sequential N+1 [listFiles()](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/ShadowVault/lib/aleo/programState.ts#52-65) | ✅ Fixed | Uses `Promise.all()` for parallel fetching |
| Weak 32-bit [cidToField()](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/ShadowVault/lib/aleo/encode.ts#1-16) hash | ✅ Fixed | Replaced with SHA-256 (248 bits) |
| No file size limit | ✅ Fixed | 50MB max enforced client-side |
| IPFS API keys exposed client-side | ✅ Fixed | Server-side `/api/upload` route; `PINATA_JWT` is server-only |
| No Error Boundary | ✅ Fixed | [ErrorBoundary](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/ShadowVault/components/ErrorBoundary.tsx#15-46) wraps [Providers](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/ShadowVault/components/Providers.tsx#21-35) |
| No skeleton loaders | ✅ Fixed | [Skeleton](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/ShadowVault/components/Skeleton.tsx#1-9) and [FileCardSkeleton](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/ShadowVault/components/Skeleton.tsx#10-24) components added |
| No Aleo address validation | ✅ Fixed | [isValidAleoAddress()](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/ShadowVault/lib/aleo/validate.ts#3-6) with regex validation |
| No confirmation dialogs | ✅ Fixed | `confirm()` before grant/revoke |
| Inconsistent layout (Footer inside main) | ✅ Fixed | Shared [(app)/layout.tsx](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/ShadowVault/app/api/upload/route.ts#5-49) with Header + Footer |
| No "Copy CID" button | ✅ Fixed | Owner can copy CID on file detail page |
| No env validation | ✅ Fixed | [lib/env.ts](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/ShadowVault/lib/env.ts) with [validateEnv()](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/ShadowVault/lib/env.ts#1-20) |
| Unused `ipfs-http-client` dependency | ✅ Fixed | Removed from [package.json](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/ShadowVault/package.json) |

