## 🏗️ Section 4: Architecture Issues

### Still Remaining

| Issue | Description |
|---|---|
| **No mobile navigation** | Header links break on small screens — no hamburger/drawer menu |
| **No toast notifications** | Success/error still inline text only |
| **`set_price` not accessible in UI** | Contract supports it but no page/button for it |
| **Settings page is bare** | Only shows address and disconnect — no actual settings |
| **No password strength indicator** | Encryption password field has no feedback |
| **Price field accepts non-numeric input** | `<input type="text">` for price — should validate numeric input |
| **No "view as buyer" experience** | File detail page is confusing for non-owners — unclear how to buy |

### Fixed ✅

| Issue | Resolution |
|---|---|
| Shared layout | `(app)/layout.tsx` with consistent Header + Footer |
| Error boundary | Wraps all providers |
| Skeleton loaders | Used on marketplace, my-files, purchased, file detail pages |

